metadata.name: Light out of Darkness
metadata.description:
"While I was at Yas Shopping Mall in Abu Dhabi. I spotted the fine reflection of the ornate glass ceiling on the floor giving it a lovely pattern. I figured it would be nice to have a subject in this composition, so I waited until the couple had passed. It turned to be an amazing combination (Shadows, silhouette and the floor). I knew this image would stand out because of the good contrast and composition‚Äù
I took this photo with my iPhone 12 Pro Max
